scoringPlays.text: Brian Herrien 2 Yd Run (Rodrigo Blankenship Kick)
Charlie Woerner 20 Yd pass from Jake Fromm (Rodrigo Blankenship Kick)
Tyler Davis 6 Yd pass from James Graham (Brenton King Kick)
Tyler Simmons 17 Yd pass from Jake Fromm (Rodrigo Blankenship Kick)
George Pickens 41 Yd pass from Jake Fromm (Rodrigo Blankenship Kick)
Dominick Blaylock 9 Yd pass from Jake Fromm (Rodrigo Blankenship Kick)
Kenny McIntosh 2 Yd Run (Rodrigo Blankenship Kick)
Tyson Campbell 0 Yd Fumble Return (Rodrigo Blankenship Kick)

videos.description: Brian Herrien takes the handoff and pounds his way through the defense to score a two-yard Georgia touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia's Herrien runs in a 2-yard TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia's Herrien runs in a 2-yard TD

videos.description: Charlie Woerner catches the pass from Jake Fromm and scores a 20-yard touchdown to give Georgia a 17-0 lead over Georgia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fromm connects with Woerner for 20-yard score) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fromm connects with Woerner for 20-yard score

videos.description: James Graham completes a pass to Tyler Davis who dives for the pylon to score a six-yard Georgia Tech touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia Tech's Davis dives to score 6-yard TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Davis dives to score 6-yard TD

videos.description: Georgia Tech recovers the onside kick by Brenton King and head coach Geoff Collins drops down to do pushups to celebrate.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (GA Tech coach Collins celebrates onside kick recovery with push-ups) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: GA Tech coach Collins celebrates onside kick recovery with pushups

videos.description: Georgia's Dominick Blaylock lets the ball slips through his hands on the punt return and Georgia Tech's Tyler Cooksey comes up with the recovery.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia Tech recovers on Georgia muffed punt return) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia Tech recovers on Georgia muffed punt return

videos.description: Jake Fromm goes over the top and connects with a leaping Tyler Simmons to score a 17-yard Georgia touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Simmons leaps to make TD catch over defender) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons leaps to make TD catch over defender

videos.description: D'Andre Swift attempts to pitch a pass forward but fumbles the ball when he's taken down in the red zone. Swift suffers an apparent arm injury on the play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Swift injured after fumbling in the red zone) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Swift injured after fumbling in the red zone

videos.description: Jake Fromm completes a pass to George Pickens for a 41-yard touchdown to give Georgia a 31-7 lead over Georgia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fromm connects with Pickens for 41-yard TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fromm connects with Pickens for 41-yard TD

videos.description: While Dominick Blaylock scores on a nine-yard touchdown pass from Jake Fromm, George Pickens and Tre Swilling brawl on the opposite side of the field, resulting in Pickens' ejection.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Blaylock scores while Pickens and Swilling throw punches out of bounds) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Blaylock scores while Pickens and Swilling throw punches out of bounds

videos.description: In game that features four Jake Fromm touchdown passes, a plethora of turnovers and a fight, Georgia comes out on top over Georgia Tech 52-7 during rivalry week.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (From throws 4 TD passes as Georgia dominates GA Tech) 2019/11/30 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: From throws 4 TD passes as Georgia dominates GA Tech
